      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * AAAI</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:290px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Artificial_Intelligence.svg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/7b/Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Artificial_Intelligence.svg.png\" width=\"288\" height=\"204\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Artificial_Intelligence.svg.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>AAAI Logo <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>AAAI</b>, <br />\nthe <b>Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</b> is a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Non-profit_organization\">nonprofit</a> scientific society devoted to advancing the scientific understanding of the mechanisms underlying thought and <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">intelligent behavior</a> and their embodiment in machines. AAAI was founded in 1979 under the name <i>American Association for Artificial Intelligence</i> and changed its name in 2007 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> .\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Presidents\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Presidents</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications_and_Journals\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications and Journals</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Presidents\">Presidents</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=AAAI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Presidents\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Since 1985, Presidents have served a two-year term, preceded by two years as President-Elect, and followed by two years as Past President. Prior to that time, presidents served one year in each position <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> .\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> President\n</th>\n<th> term\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Allen_Newell\" title=\"Allen Newell\">Allen Newell</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1979-1980\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Edward_Feigenbaum\" title=\"Edward Feigenbaum\">Edward Feigenbaum</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1980-1981\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Marvin_Minsky\" title=\"Marvin Minsky\">Marvin Minsky</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1981-1982\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#NilsNilsson\" title=\"Mathematician\">Nils J. Nilsson</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1982-1983\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/John_McCarthy\" title=\"John McCarthy\">John McCarthy</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1983-1984\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Woodrow_W._Bledsoe\" title=\"Woodrow W. Bledsoe\">Woodrow W. Bledsoe</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1984-1985\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Patrick_Winston\" title=\"Patrick Winston\">Patrick Winston</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1985-1987\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#RajReddy\" title=\"Mathematician\">Raj Reddy</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1987-1989\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#DGBobrow\" title=\"Mathematician\">Daniel Bobrow</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1989-1991\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#PHayes\" title=\"Mathematician\">Patrick Hayes</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1991-1993\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#BJGrosz\" title=\"Mathematician\">Barbara Grosz</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1993-1995\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#RDavis\" title=\"Mathematician\">Randall Davis</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1995-1997\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/David_Waltz\" title=\"David Waltz\">David Waltz</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1997-1999\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#BGBuchanan\" title=\"Mathematician\">Bruce Buchanan</a>\n</td>\n<td>  1999-2001\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Tom_Mitchell\" title=\"Tom Mitchell\">Tom Mitchell</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2001-2003\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ronald_J._Brachman\">Ron Brachman</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2003-2005\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alan_Mackworth\">Alan Mackworth</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2005-2007\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#EJHorvitz\" title=\"Mathematician\">Eric Horvitz</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2007-2009\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#MEPollack\" title=\"Mathematician\">Martha E. Pollack</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2009-2010\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#HAKautz\" title=\"Mathematician\">Henry A. Kautz</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2010-2012\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Manuela_Veloso\" title=\"Manuela Veloso\">Manuela M. Veloso</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2012-2014\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#TDietterich\" title=\"Mathematician\">Thomas G. Dietterich</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2014-2016\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>  <a href=\"/Mathematician#SKambhampati\" title=\"Mathematician\">Subbarao Kambhampati</a>\n</td>\n<td>  2017\n</td></tr></table>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=AAAI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Conferences#AAAI\" title=\"Conferences\">AAAI Workshops</a></li></ul>\n<p><span id=\"Publications\"></span>\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications_and_Journals\">Publications and Journals</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=AAAI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications and Journals\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Publications/publications.php\">AAAI Publications</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"AIMAG\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Library/Magazine/magazine-library.php\">AAAI Digital Library - AI Magazine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Publications/Journals/sponsored-journals.php\">AAAI Sponsored Journals</a></li>\n<li> <span id=\"Press\"></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Press/press.php\">AAAI Press</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=AAAI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Edward_Feigenbaum\" title=\"Edward Feigenbaum\">Edward Feigenbaum</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/ojs/index.php/aimagazine/article/view/1840\">Stories of AAAI - Before the Beginning and After: A Love Letter</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.aaai.org/ojs/index.php/aimagazine/index\">AI Magazine</a>, Vol. 26, No. 4</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=AAAI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Artificial_Intelligence\">Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/home.html\">Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Conferences/conferences.php\">AAAI Conferences</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Organization/officers.php\">AAAI Officials</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=AAAI&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Logo of Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Association_for_the_Advancement_of_Artificial_Intelligence\">Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Organization/name-change.php\">AAAI Name Change</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aaai.org/Organization/past-officers.php\">AAAI Past Officers</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301053944\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 72/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 148/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:2087-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301053944 and revision id 8921\n -->\n"
